diff:1430420629:1430185160:minor=15d14%0a%3c *[[http://ragnarok.gamingsandbox.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=9&t=983 | Atlanteans]] are allowed.  Click the link for details.%0a29,33c28,32%0a%3c The “bottom” of the skill pyramid is raised to Good (+3) instead of Average (+1).%0a%3c %0a%3c What this means is that for the purposes of checking the balance of your skill pyramid, you only have to look at Good (+3) skills and up. Average (+1) and Fair (+2) skills are no longer required to support your skill pyramid.%0a%3c %0a%3c This does not mean Average (+1) skills are bumped up to Fair (+2) or Fair (+2) are bumped up to Good (+3). To raise a skill from Mediocre (+0) to Good (+3), you must still spend 3 skill points like normal. You can still have Average (+1) and Fair (+2) skills—they just don’t apply to pyramid balance.%0a---%0a> The “bottom” of the skill pyramid is raised to Fair (+2) instead of Average (+1).%0a> %0a> What this means is that for the purposes of checking the balance of your skill pyramid, you only have to look at Fair (+2) skills and up. Average (+1) skills are no longer required to support your skill pyramid.%0a> %0a> This does not mean Average (+1) skills are bumped up to Fair (+2). To raise a skill from Mediocre (+0) to Fair (+2), you must still spend 2 skill points like normal. You can still have Average (+1) skills—they just don’t apply to pyramid balance.%0a
